g2:c.FUNCTION-DEFINITION.g2:a.TEXT: upp-is-client-connected (client) = (if ((the ui-client-connection-status of client does not exist) or (the ui-client-connection-status of client exists and the ui-client-connection-status of client is connected)) then true else false)

g2:c.RULE.g2:a.TEXT: whenever the uil-package-name of any uil-title-block TB receives a value then conclude that the package of the icon-variables of TB = the uil-package-name of TB
whenever the uil-module-title of any uil-title-block TB receives a value then conclude that the module-name of the icon-variables of TB = the uil-module-title of TB
whenever the uil-title-block-width of any uil-title-block TB receives a value then conclude that the width of the icon-variables of TB = the uil-title-block-width of TB
whenever any uil-navigation-button-template B is moved by the user then start upp-make-navigation-button(B)

g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: uil-convert-button-from-4.1-to-5.0 (B: class uil-button) other-conversion-proc: symbol = the symbol upp-convert-button-from-4.1-to-5.0; begin if (the procedure named by other-conversion-proc exists) then call the procedure named by other-conversion-proc (B) else call upp-convert-navigation-button-from-4.1-to-5.0 (B); end

g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.LABEL: CONVERT-TO-50R0-BUTTON
g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.CONDITION: the uil-label-id of the item /= "5.0" and the uil-size of the item exists and not (is-contained-in-text ("msw", "[the uil-size of the item]"))

g2:c.RULE.g2:a.TEXT: whenever the label of any uil-navigation-button B receives a value and when (the uil-label-id of B exists and the uil-label-id of B = "5.0") then start upp-update-button-label (B)

g2:c.FUNCTION-DEFINITION.g2:a.TEXT: baseline-depth-for-font-size (size) = (if size = the symbol small then 10 else if size = the symbol large then 18 else 13)

c.UIL-SMALL-TEXT.g2:a.TEXT: This should be copied shamelessly from g2-get-text-extent. Make sure it's up-to-date.
c.UIL-SMALL-TEXT.ua.MESSAGE-CONTENTS: This should be copied shamelessly from g2-get-text-extent. Make sure it's up-to-date.

g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.LABEL: SELECT
g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.CONDITION: the state of the item is enabled and the class of the item is not uil-radio-button and the class of the item is not uil-text-pushbutton
g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.ACTION: start upp-select-workspace-button (the item, this window, ({if the item O superior to the workspace of the item exists and O is a uil-dialog then O else} the workspace of the item)) at priority uil-global-default-procedure-priority

g2:c.RULE.g2:a.TEXT: whenever any uil-button B is moved by the user then start upp-move-button (B, true)

g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: uil-delete-navigation-button(b:class uil-navigation-button) begin call upp-delete-navigation-button-method (b); end

g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.LABEL: SELECT
g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.CONDITION: the state of the item is enabled and the class of the item is not uil-radio-button and the class of the item is not uil-text-pushbutton
g2:c.USER-MENU-CHOICE.g2:a.ACTION: start uil-select-navigation-button (the item, this window, ({if the item O superior to the workspace of the item exists and O is a uil-dialog then O else} the workspace of the item)) at priority uil-global-default-procedure-priority
